recommendation engine project
"develop your personal eye"

- synthetic interaction generation until real users accumulated
- model training (svd, als, neural cf, two-tower --- compare ndcg@k and pick
best)
- baselines + evaluation metrics (ndcg, precision@k, MAP)
- experiment tracking (mlflow, diff models + hyperparams)
- offline evaluations
- serving (fastapi + model registry)

hybrid:
- CLIP embeddings for all artworks
- filtering on user interactions (behavioral)
- hybrid blending layer (weight content-based higher for new users to combat cold start then shift to filtering once behavioral data)

stretch:
- allow artists to upload their own art
- segments once behavioral data
